ared\" target=\"_blank\">on their drServer site</a>.</p><table style=\"height: 265px\" width=\"650\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Xen HVM S Plan Dallas</strong><p></p><ul><li>2 CPU Cores</li><li>1024 MB RAM</li><li>20 GB SSD Disk</li><li>1024 GB Bandwidth</li><li>1 IPv4</li><li>/64 IPv6</li><li>Xen HVM</li><li>Linux/Windows</li><li>5 EUR/mo ~=$5.34/mo</li><li>60 EUR/year</li><li>[<a href=\"https://vikinglayer.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=91\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>Xen HVM S Plan Buffalo</strong><p></p><ul><li>2 CPU Cores</li><li>1024 MB RAM</li><li>20 GB SSD Disk</li><li>1024 GB Bandwidth</li><li>1 IPv4</li><li>Xen HVM</li><li>Linux/Windows</li><li>5 EUR/mo ~=$5.34/mo</li><li>60 EUR/yr</li><li>[<a href=\"https://vikinglayer.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=93\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td><td valign=\"top\"><strong>1 GB RAM Promo Sweden</strong><p></p><ul><li>4 Cores</li><li>1 GB RAM</li><li>30 GB RAID10 HDD</li><li>1 TB @ 1 Gbit</li><li>1 IPv4</li><li>/64 IPv6</li><li>OpenVZ/Linux</li><li></li><li>20 EUR/year ~= $21.36/year</li><li>[<a href=\"https://vikinglayer.com/clients/cart.php?a=add&amp;pid=109\">Order Now</a>]</li></ul></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span id=\"more-9672\"></span></p><p><strong>Network info:</strong></p><p><strong>Dallas, Incero</strong></p><div>Test IPv4: 192.138.210.63</div><div>Test IPv6: 2604:0880:0052:0000:0000:0000:01e5:657b</div><div>Test file: <a href=\"http://lg.dal.vikinglayer.com/100MB.test\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://lg.dal.vikinglayer.com/100MB.test</a></div><div>Looking glass: <a href=\"http://lg.dal.vikinglayer.com/\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://lg.dal.vikinglayer.com</a></div><div><strong>Buffalo, ColoCrossing</strong></div><div>Test IPv4: 192.227.187.104</div><div>Test IPv6: Not available</div><div>Test file: <a href=\"http://lg.buf.vikinglayer.com/100MB.test\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://lg.buf.vikinglayer.com/100MB.test</a></div><div>Looking glass: <a href=\"http://lg.buf.viking